172
00:10:25,980 --> 00:10:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

173
00:10:27,610 --> 00:10:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, you really hate losing.</font>

174
00:10:30,440 --> 00:10:33,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stuff happened in my past,</font>

175
00:10:33,450 --> 00:10:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and now I can't sing my 
original songs in front of people.</font>

176
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:38,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Elaborate.</font>

177
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm scared.</font>

178
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of the looks people give me when 
they judge me or think I'm a letdown.</font>

179
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Covers are much easier because I can 
hide behind other people's music.</font>

180
00:10:50,530 --> 00:10:51,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How cowardly, right?</font>

181
00:10:52,650 --> 00:10:56,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. She's scared of the 
audience's judgmental eyes?</i></font>

182
00:10:56,370 --> 00:11:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A straightforward trauma, 
and a critical one.</i></font>

183
00:11:00,450 --> 00:11:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If it's not resolved at once, 
she has no future.</i></font>

184
00:11:03,150 --> 00:11:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been trying to write a new song,</font>

185
00:11:05,820 --> 00:11:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but remembering those eyes 
stops me dead in my tracks.</font>

186
00:11:09,010 --> 00:11:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's affecting her songwriting, too.</i></font>

187
00:11:11,470 --> 00:11:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What should I do?</i></font>

188
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right. We'll just have to 
do this the Yamabuki way.</i></font>

189
00:11:17,410 --> 00:11:19,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're scared of having eyes on you?</font>

190
00:11:19,870 --> 00:11:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I used to be that way, too.</font>

191
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:24,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that's my tea, right?</font>

192
00:11:24,740 --> 00:11:27,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had to take part in numerous 
extracurricular activities.</font>

193
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Presentations and speeches 
were part of that.</font>

194
00:11:31,640 --> 00:11:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The piercing gaze of the audience 
is something I know all too well.</font>

195
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you get over your fear?</font>

196
00:11:40,100 --> 00:11:41,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you can't write a new song,</font>

197
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you still have your old ones, right?</font>

198
00:11:43,810 --> 00:11:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? I guess?</font>

199
00:11:47,210 --> 00:11:48,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then it's clear what we must do.</font>

200
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:52,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll do an "Inohana Rikka 
Original Songs School Concert."</font>

201
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha?</font>

202
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:57,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You just have to get used to it. 
Experience is everything.</font>

203
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:59,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll arrange a venue 
and an audience.</font>

204
00:11:59,330 --> 00:12:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't decide for me!</font>

205
00:12:00,850 --> 00:12:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It doesn't have to be a new song, 
but you can only perform your own songs.</font>

206
00:12:05,590 --> 00:12:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think you're being 
a bit insensitive?</font>

207
00:12:08,210 --> 00:12:12,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is normal for the Yamabuki family. 
Even you should be able to do it.</font>

208
00:12:14,370 --> 00:12:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, fine.</font>

209
00:12:15,540 --> 00:12:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excellent. Now, as for when...</font>

210
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:20,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll do the concert a week from now!</font>

211
00:12:25,590 --> 00:12:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The school rooftop? 
Why not my usual spot?</i></font>

212
00:12:30,340 --> 00:12:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought you'd understand how I feel, 
but I guess I was wrong.</i></font>

213
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In the end, you're not mediocre like me.</i></font>

214
00:12:41,630 --> 00:12:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are you the same as that guy?</i></font>

215
00:12:44,950 --> 00:12:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought you'd be up for it.</font>

216
00:12:47,700 --> 00:12:49,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I expected too much of you.</font>

217
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:07,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, Yamabuki-kun. 
I really don't think I can...</font>

218
00:13:07,520 --> 00:13:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you're finally here.</font>

219
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rooftop scary!</font>

220
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:13,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We get to hear your original song 
after so long, Rikka-chan!</font>

221
00:13:14,040 --> 00:13:15,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

222
00:13:15,730 --> 00:13:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why are you all here? 
Where are the other spectators?</font>

223
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:21,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just the four of us.</font>

224
00:13:21,110 --> 00:13:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you really think 
I'd throw you to the wolves?</font>

225
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In order to get used to 
the audience's gaze,</font>

226
00:13:25,450 --> 00:13:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you start with friends and family.</font>

227
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've just told us 
if we could help you overcome it.</font>

228
00:13:32,880 --> 00:13:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll watch you 
with the clearest of eyes.</font>

229
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We get VIP seats! That's so cool!</font>

230
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:44,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relax. I've locked the door.</font>

231
00:13:44,180 --> 00:13:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have nothing but allies here. 
Shake your fear and sing for us.</font>

232
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FURIN HIGH SCHOOL</font>

233
00:13:53,040 --> 00:13:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, uh...</font>

234
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been ages since I last played 
my songs for you, huh?</font>

235
00:13:58,630 --> 00:14:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, damn...</font>

236
00:14:00,570 --> 00:14:02,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't even know what to say.</font>

237
00:14:02,700 --> 00:14:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did I wrongly assume that she'd be 
able to do it in front of friends?</i></font>

238
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:10,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It seems her trauma is quite 
deep-rooted. What do I do now?</i></font>

239
00:14:11,110 --> 00:14:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry...</font>

240
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka!</font>

241
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rikka-chan!</font>

242
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:22,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}RIKKA FTW - WE STAN INOHANA</font>

243
00:14:16,970 --> 00:14:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You always put up a front 
and never tell us anything.</font>

244
00:14:20,370 --> 00:14:22,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should at least vent to us sometimes.</font>

245
00:14:22,670 --> 00:14:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}RIKKA</font>

246
00:14:22,930 --> 00:14:27,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We kinda made these sloppy last-minute, 
but we'll do better when it's for reals.</font>

247
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:31,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}RIKKA LOVE</font>

248
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:31,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Imagine we're always in the front row.</font>

249
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:35,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just look at us when it gets tough, okay?</font>

250
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:42,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, okay.</font>

251
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to be a singer, Rikka-chan?</font>

252
00:14:54,620 --> 00:14:57,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you take the stage 
at the Tokyo Dome someday?</font>

253
00:14:57,810 --> 00:15:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanna see you sing in a huge venue.</font>

254
00:14:58,820 --> 00:15:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}As we looked up the open blue sky</i></font>

255
00:15:01,290 --> 00:15:04,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pull some strings 
and get us front-row seats.</font>

256
00:15:03,290 --> 00:15:06,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In bright white letters</i></font>

257
00:15:04,520 --> 00:15:07,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'd be great! 
Close enough to see your face!</font>

258
00:15:06,560 --> 00:15:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We wrote about our purpose, 
we wrote about our future</i></font>

259
00:15:08,460 --> 00:15:12,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Right... I'd made a promise.</i></font>

260
00:15:11,040 --> 00:15:14,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And painted it with your dreams</i></font>

261
00:15:13,480 --> 00:15:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That I'd get them front-row 
seats to my concert.</i></font>

262
00:15:14,770 --> 00:15:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}With each passing "See you tomorrow"</i></font>

263
00:15:20,040 --> 00:15:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Our hearts grew closer</i></font>

264
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:30,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe you tricked me. 
Way to destroy my trust in you.</font>

265
00:15:30,410 --> 00:15:34,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry. I figured you wouldn't be 
nervous if I told you in advance.</font>

266
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apology rejected.</font>

267
00:15:36,410 --> 00:15:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I redeem myself?</font>

268
00:15:40,130 --> 00:15:43,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Treat me to karaoke and help me practice.</font>

269
00:15:43,180 --> 00:15:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that'll repair your trust, sure.</font>

270
00:15:45,690 --> 00:15:48,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One time probably isn't enough, though.</font>

271
00:15:48,040 --> 00:15:50,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did my credit score go down that much?!</font>

272
00:15:50,300 --> 00:15:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What's it at right now?</font>

273
00:15:55,420 --> 00:15:58,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it was at 100 before, 
it's around 80 now.</font>

274
00:15:58,870 --> 00:16:00,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It fell 20 points!</font>

275
00:16:00,940 --> 00:16:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}20 POINTS IS BASICALLY THE MARGIN OF ERROR</font>

276
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:07,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}In the middle of outer space</i></font>

277
00:16:07,310 --> 00:16:12,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}We seize our very own reason 
that we can only find here</i></font>

278
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It starts running and running</i></font>

279
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That song, which she probably 
wrote a long time ago,</i></font>

280
00:16:14,590 --> 00:16:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Becoming a nameless warmth in our hearts</i></font>

281
00:16:16,610 --> 00:16:20,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>was rough around the edges 
but very Inohana.</i></font>

282
00:16:20,370 --> 00:16:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}And our world</i></font>

283
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And it definitely touched hearts, 
even if crying was a bit over the top.</i></font>

284
00:16:27,570 --> 00:16:32,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have no idea why she locked 
that talent away,</i></font>

285
00:16:33,560 --> 00:16:37,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but she's taken a step forward 
thanks to her clubmates.</i></font>

286
00:16:40,760 --> 00:16:46,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought I could guide them myself, 
but that was hubris on yours truly's part.</i></font>

287
00:16:48,010 --> 00:16:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When they run into adversity one day,</i></font>

288
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>it probably won't be me 
who helps them overcome it,</i></font>

289
00:16:55,560 --> 00:16:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but rather the bonds between them.</i></font>

290
00:17:02,470 --> 00:17:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With that in mind,</font>

291
00:17:04,360 --> 00:17:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">why don't you four hang out and have 
fun together to bolster your solidarity?</font>

292
00:17:09,360 --> 00:17:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the shopping mall?</font>

293
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:12,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My little sister loves this place.</font>

294
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to buy something here?</font>

295
00:17:13,510 --> 00:17:15,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to get sneakers 
for my little sister.</font>

296
00:17:15,410 --> 00:17:18,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why'd you pick somewhere so far away?</font>

297
00:17:18,390 --> 00:17:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This place has good parfaits, 
or so my little sister said.</font>

298
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sis this, Sis that! Come with her, then!</font>

299
00:17:22,900 --> 00:17:26,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We haven't been hanging out 
a lot lately, huh?</font>

300
00:17:26,050 --> 00:17:28,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prepping for sports day 
kept us all busy.</font>

301
00:17:28,700 --> 00:17:30,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to get some new clothes!</font>

302
00:17:30,740 --> 00:17:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feel free to have fun however. 
Pay no mind to yours errand boy truly.</font>

303
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:35,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care about you by default.</font>

304
00:17:35,930 --> 00:17:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, wait!</font>

305
00:17:37,460 --> 00:17:39,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to have some fun together.</font>

306
00:17:40,500 --> 00:17:42,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Mr. Errand Boy.</font>

307
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're free, help me pick out clothes?</font>

308
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:47,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind, but wouldn't it be better 
to ask the girls instead?</font>

309
00:17:47,910 --> 00:17:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, actually,</font>

310
00:17:49,590 --> 00:17:51,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've put on weight lately.</font>

311
00:17:51,390 --> 00:17:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want them to know.</font>

312
00:17:54,040 --> 00:17:56,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's okay if I know?</font>

313
00:17:57,020 --> 00:17:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yamabuki-kun.</font>

314
00:17:58,350 --> 00:17:59,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get going.</font>

315
00:18:03,260 --> 00:18:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think of this?</font>

316
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about this?</font>

317
00:18:08,090 --> 00:18:09,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is this a bit too showy?</font>

318
00:18:10,110 --> 00:18:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Balanced, but less isn't always more. 
Seventy-eight points.</font>

319
00:18:14,630 --> 00:18:17,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't expect you to 
try this hard to help me.</font>

320
00:18:17,200 --> 00:18:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway,</font>

321
00:18:18,330 --> 00:18:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you've only tried on white clothes.</font>

322
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I like white.</font>

323
00:18:22,940 --> 00:18:25,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm wearing a white outfit right now.</i></font>

324
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I like white, you see.</i></font>

325
00:18:27,040 --> 00:18:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Come to think of it, 
Apollo said something similar.</i></font>

326
00:18:31,010 --> 00:18:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I keep seeing traces of Apollo 
in these girls every now and then,</i></font>

327
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I still lack conclusive proof.</i></font>

328
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A lot of people like the color white...</i></font>

329
00:18:39,500 --> 00:18:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, tell me.</font>

330
00:18:40,980 --> 00:18:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does your silence mean 
that you like this showy outfit?</font>

331
00:18:46,070 --> 00:18:47,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As if!</font>

332
00:18:47,000 --> 00:18:49,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, it's the best one so far.</font>

333
00:18:49,870 --> 00:18:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look very cute.</font>

334
00:18:51,160 --> 00:18:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cu...</font>

335
00:18:53,330 --> 00:18:56,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I didn't ask you to go into 
that much detail...</font>

336
00:18:59,540 --> 00:19:02,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, where did the other three go?</font>

337
00:19:02,620 --> 00:19:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bucky! Help!</font>

338
00:19:06,830 --> 00:19:09,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's an emergency! 
Come with me right now!</font>

339
00:19:11,130 --> 00:19:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's stuck in the chute! 
After I spent 1,000 yen, too!</font>

340
00:19:14,720 --> 00:19:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you want me to get it out?</font>

341
00:19:16,630 --> 00:19:18,930
